[src:matrix-chain-multiplication/dynamic-programming] Using dynamic programming in the calculation of the *n*th member of the Fibonacci sequence improves its performance greatly.
[src:matrix-chain-multiplication/dynamic-programming] In particular, `fib(2)` was calculated three times from scratch.
