[src:matrix-chain-multiplication/dynamic-programming] The process terminates either when there are no more test eggs (*n* = 0) or when *k* = 0, whichever occurs first.
[src:matrix-chain-multiplication/dynamic-programming] If termination occurs at state *s* = (0,*k*) and *k* > 0, then the test failed.
